---
title: Nicoise-Inspired Salmon on Herby Orzo with Tomatoes and Olives
description: This take on Salade Nicoise is speedy and substantial! Marinated tomatoes, briny olives and succulent salmon top a bed of herby orzo with parsley, arugula and spinach.
